
====manual====
- switch to edit mode 
- select all faces
- ?select main object to trace with polygon?
- edge split on all faces of python
- separate faces by loose parts
==============

- origin to center of mass on each face
- for each face
    - copy location of face
    - isolate longest edge
    - separate longest edge as direction vector
    - longest edge is now selected
    - set longest

-iterate through faces again
    - delete each face
    
- for each edge, assuming faces are all deleted
    - make a duplicate of snake scale object
    - match location of snake scale to face
    - to_track_quat scale duplicate to durectuib vector
    
